Ash Hartwell was an early [[Peace Corps]] volunteer in various posts in Africa and then moved back to the United States. He became a student of [[Dwight W. Allen]] on reforming university educational programs, learned and joined the Bah<U+00E1>'<U+00ED> Faith, and then returned to Africa. Eventually his family moved to Botswana.<ref>{{cite episode
